  "title": "Valentine's Florist assistant (Ad-Hoc)",
  "description": "<p>📌 <strong>Job Details</strong></p><p>Role: Valentine’s Day Ad-Hoc Part-Time Crew<br /></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p>- Basic floral assembly*</p><p>- Floral bouquet preparation*</p><p>- Flower maintenance*</p><p>- Other ad-hoc tasks (e.g. sorting orders, handling flowers)</p><p>*On-the-job training will be provided</p><p></p><p><strong>👤 Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Quick to adapt and learn</li><li>Positive working attitude and willingness to take initiative</li><li>Able to stand for the duration of the shift</li><li>Basic Floral Experience preferred</li></ul><p>📅<strong> Work Period & Hours</strong></p><p>- 7 – 15 February 2026</p><p>- 10:00am – 9:00pm</p><p></p><p>We are looking for staff who can commit to at least one half-shift (4 hours) per day, for a minimum of 2 consecutive days.</p><p></p><p>Preference will be given to those who can work closer to Valentine’s Day (12–15 Feb).</p><p>Example: 2pm–9pm on 12, 13 & 14 Feb</p><p>💰 <strong>Remuneration</strong><br />$12–$15 per hour, depending on prior floristry experience and on-the-job competency.<br /></p><p>If you’re interested, please:<br />1) WhatsApp us at 8859 7170<br />2) Send us a short self introduction & your available dates and timings.</p><p>Should you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at 88597170😊</p>",
